reviewText: If you are into plastic breasts and plastic plots, you will enjoy this.  This is not even near the quality of other movies based on "Lady Chatterly's Lover" in plot, acting or any other way.  We will probably give it to Goodwill or a local library.
I liked it for obvious reasons...and you will like it too for the same reasons.  Was worth 15 bucks and I watch it at least once a week.
